body:
@tjatjagithub This will be fixed in the upcoming 0.10 release as long as you have

```yml
mouse_bindings:
  - { mouse: Right, action: Paste }
```

in your configuration file.

@tmpm697 What version of Alacritty are you using and what platform? I'm using 0.10.1 on Linux and it is working for me.  I just tested again and the following sequence works:

- Select text using the left mouse button to click and drag or by double-clicking on a word.
- Right-click anywhere in the window and the text is pasted.  This can be repeated, too.
